"Leta•zip | URL Shortener" is a practical Chrome browser extension that seamlessly integrates the Leta•zip service directly into your web browser. This extension provides you with a hassle-free way to compress and share links in a simple and speedy manner.

With "Leta•zip | URL Shortener," you can bid farewell to complex procedures for shortening and sharing links. A single mouse click is all it takes, and your long, unreadable link instantly transforms into a concise, easily shareable one. This approach not only saves you time but also streamlines the link-sharing process with friends, colleagues, or on social media platforms.
